cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.RO 

This paper combines deep reinforcement learning with visual selective attention, which involves both computer vision and machine learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also discusses the learning process and optimization techniques, which could fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.RO (Robotics).
